that various stages of progress can be tracked on-line. Even for recruitmen=
t, companies can track the chosen projects
 if allowed by the respective students and faculty team and thus select bri=
ght hard working teams. They can pose their problems at the portal too. Eac=
h university can develop its own tracking system if it so wishes.</span></f=
ont></p>
